lead_paragraph: Monte Morris had 18 points and six assists and No. 19 Iowa State followed a win over top-ranked Oklahoma with a 73-60 victory over TCU on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: No. 19 Iowa State Tops TCU 73-60 After Beating Top-Ranked OU
